  <div class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="habitationSaveOptionsTitle" aria-hidden="true" data-save-state-target="modal" data-habitation-save-options-modal="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="habitationSaveOptionsTitle">Como deseja salvar?</h5>
          <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Fechar"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <p class="mb-0 text-muted">
            Escolha se quer continuar editando esta ficha ou voltar para o catálogo depois que o imóvel for salvo.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer flex-column flex-sm-row align-items-stretch align-items-sm-center">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-habitation-save-options-action="cancel">
            Cancelar
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary" data-habitation-save-options-action="stay">
            Salvar e permanecer
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-habitation-save-options-action="exit">
            Salvar e sair
